data.description: Welcome Home to this beautiful house in Ellington Village!   This spacious home offers over 2200 square feet of living space!  Including 4 oversized bedrooms;  large family room, and a first floor office!   The owner's suite includes tray ceilings, two walk-in closets, a glass door shower, and dual sinks!   The kitchen has tons of prep room and an island which is perfect for entertaining!   You'll love all the space in the family room with a gas fireplace!  Outside you have 0.32 aces on a corner lot!  The backyard is fenced in!  Enjoy summer bbqs and sunsets while sitting on the stone patio!   Plus there is a community pool!  Don't miss this amazing home!   Schedule your showing today!
